For the third step, assuming all the S samples are classified into l clusters and the t-th cluster contains St samples, we have \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
